Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was careless.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.06,0:00:08.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I deployed some personnel\N in the area around this house.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.42,0:00:11.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But they struck when \Nshe happened to be over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing left at the scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.97,0:00:18.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They took her while she was using the bathroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.09,0:00:19.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is because...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is because I brought Sana{-chan} here!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.00,0:00:24.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun} and a lady named\N Yamada are after them now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.85,0:00:32.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll find her soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.46,0:00:34.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.42,0:00:35.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.32,0:00:38.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.30,0:00:47.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana{-chan} is valuable to those guys, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They won't be quick to harm her.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Harm her?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sanae...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.33,0:01:03.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you just imagine it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.48,0:01:09.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you struggle or disobey me, you will die.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I would do absolutely anything
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.01,0:01:16.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to see him again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What does everyone like about such a noisy place?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to go home and play video games.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We're done here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.55,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.55,0:03:12.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We can leave the rest to Minnie C.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll bring the Red Queen home.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.16,0:03:17.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You all did great.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.99,0:03:21.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you get hungry before we get there,\N you can have that—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.57,0:03:22.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.88,0:03:25.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of sweet stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When this is over, \Neverything will be back to normal, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll be with Sana{-chan} again.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.01,0:03:32.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you disappoint me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.39,0:03:49.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You once commanded the principles of space itself.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.75,0:03:54.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If this is all you can do outside,\Nyou really are no more than a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.97,0:03:59.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You acquired a body, learned language, \Nand gained emotions...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.38,0:04:03.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Only to flee to the outside world \Nand pretend to be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.28,0:04:08.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It was so easy to render you motionless.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretend to be human?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Or could it be...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.87,0:04:18.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you actually think you're human,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are they after that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.12,0:04:31.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I called you because I thought you could do something\Nabout the abuse she's apparently endured.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.79,0:04:36.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it looks like you guys are \Nworking on something bigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a state secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.28,0:04:39.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kidding, kidding!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's just a joke.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.84,0:04:45.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This is just something of a territorial dispute...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.68,0:04:50.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In the government, \Ntwo people have two differing opinions.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm basically one of those people's lapdog.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Say it so I can understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just what kind of little girl is she?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not sure you'll believe me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But Sana{-chan}, most likely,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,isn't a human like you and me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You are not human.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.46,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.32,0:05:20.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thirteen years ago, when you first \Nappeared beneath the research facility,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,you couldn't even be called a living thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.55,0:05:28.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You were a mere phenomenon that could \Nrandomly read thoughts and reactions
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.28,0:05:31.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,of living things around you, and make them real.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your appearance,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.40,0:05:36.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,ego, emotions, and words you learned
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,were all cards that an ownerless Mirror Gate
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.97,0:05:42.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,created by copying those things from humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a lie.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Sana, and I'm right here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.79,0:05:51.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is why you must not leave the research facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.08,0:05:54.33,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Living in the outside world is impossible for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If there is a place for you in the world,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,it is at Wonderland and nowhere else.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Now, let us return to where you belong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.23,0:06:08.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That girl's power is called a "Dream of Alice."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.56,0:06:13.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And it's said that soon, \Nmany more people will have such powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.10,0:06:16.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This may all sound preposterous.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.27,0:06:21.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But it flips our senses of vitality \Nand ethics totally upside-down.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.59,0:06:26.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can our society accept beings like her?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll soon be facing that issue head-on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, we think it's possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.62,0:06:35.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But the other side doesn't agree...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.18,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.18,0:06:43.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'd been employing various tactics\N behind the scenes already.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.13,0:06:48.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And then we learned the girl we'd \Nbeen watching had wound up with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd make use of that little godsend.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Make use of it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.33,0:07:00.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yep, to determine whether \Nhumans can coexist with Sana{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.98,0:07:07.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You've always been the kind of guy who \Ndoesn't consider the trouble he causes others.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll air my complaints later.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,After that girl comes back home.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sanae, can you continue to get along with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.91,0:07:18.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.78,0:07:21.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then the girl can—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,U-Um, that's fine, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.38,0:07:31.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa, I wish you wouldn't just\N make decisions about everything
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.69,0:07:34.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,on your own like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.44,0:07:38.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I heard that Sana{-chan} was at our house,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.20,0:07:42.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.01,0:07:47.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But you tend to be that way sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.32,0:07:54.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please value your family more!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please talk to me more!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.27,0:08:01.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If we're going to be a family of three, \Nit's all the more reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Our little chat is over.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll need you to be quiet for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not human?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.19,0:08:26.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I wasn't to go to the outside world?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I not allowed to go anywhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm a monster?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}want that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,This will just slow your body down,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,to make your brain stop working.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.19,0:08:46.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When you're completely unconscious,\N you're more dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Filthy...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.59,0:09:01.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've come here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.21,0:09:05.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It's sort of against the rules for you to talk to me.{###}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like I know you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.82,0:09:09.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.34,0:09:13.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well... let's see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.49,0:09:16.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a really cool lady you don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.71,0:09:17.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,When I was at the research facility, \Ndid you talk to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.37,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Well, in time, you'll find out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.87,0:09:26.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So flat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.73,0:09:27.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're an adult, \Nbut Sanae has bigger breasts than you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.58,0:09:33.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You'd better not forget you said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you for a loop later.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I may not be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I may be a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.49,0:09:49.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Most people don't know what they really are.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm still searching for that myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't tell you this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.85,0:09:59.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I was very lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had people around me who knew things I didn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you do, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.03,0:10:09.02,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You should try calling that person's name.
Comment: 10,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{random vocalization}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.81,0:10:16.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you just hear something?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Look above you. Above.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.34,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.58,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's Sana{-chan}'s.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.27,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Please save Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zou... roku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.27,0:10:38.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.29,0:10:52.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.76,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the first time he's called me "Sana."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.65,0:11:07.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you the one who's \Nbeen cruel to this little girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.01,0:11:10.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Red Queen,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,all you do is cause—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You demon...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.73,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.47,0:11:19.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate crooked stuff!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a florist.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.62,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But I'm not going to lose to some kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Where's your energy from earlier?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.73,0:11:34.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything, just by thinking about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.30,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't just stay here like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Get back home right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.42,0:11:49.05,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That creepy guy, Naitou, is gonna save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Get going, now!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.56,0:11:57.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Would you please be quiet?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.92,0:11:58.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.57,0:12:07.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Red Queen,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.82,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,if you try to act on your own again,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,something even worse will happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Next time, to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.13,0:12:24.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.52,0:12:26.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I am entirely serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana. Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.38,0:12:30.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.39,0:12:31.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No more!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.79,0:12:34.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did it come to this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.21,0:12:37.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm not human?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.04,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I pretended to be human when I'm not,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I called Zouroku here?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or because Zouroku and I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.07,0:12:50.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.43,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't do anything bad to Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.26,0:13:15.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Her energy finally ran out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.13,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Is your wound okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She truly is amazing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.60,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,While making her wound disappear,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she actually rewrote parts of her situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I've located Sana{-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's headed toward Oi Futo on the\N Shuto Expressway Bayshore Route!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll ask an acquaintance in Port Authority \Nif he's seen anyone strange leaving Oi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun}, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.64,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! I'll head there too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So there you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Nothing to worry about anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You should go home for now, Sanae{-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.57,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll get someone to take you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Could you take me with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.48,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.03,0:14:41.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I... really am... a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.85,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.37,0:14:46.96,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.96,0:14:48.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.23,0:14:50.41,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kashimura Zouroku{-san}, age 72.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Owner of the flower shop Kashimura Floral.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.28,0:15:03.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Your family consists of a granddaughter, \Nwho is a high school junior.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You know all about me, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it if you would\N quietly accompany us for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.80,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I am Miriam C. Tachibana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.21,0:15:22.56,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm working with a certain state project that \Ninvolves the Japanese and American governments.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The "Dreams of Alice," right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.88,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Our goal is to research the Dreams of Alice
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.98,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,and artificially reproduce their powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.98,0:15:38.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And in the end, we'll build a new \Nenergy system based upon it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.71,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You could say this is a project to benefit humanity.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.71,0:15:46.38,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't mind keeping this child locked up \Nfor life, dissecting her or anything else,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.21,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,as long as it's "to benefit humanity"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You like sci-fi movies, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We will not dissect her.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.50,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.28,0:16:01.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She is not a human, let alone a child.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.77,0:16:09.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The Red Queen is an unknown phenomenon,\Nborn when an unidentified being mimicked humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Bah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a load of nonsense to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.99,0:16:14.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She looks like an ordinary little girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.16,0:16:19.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\q2}What if a WMD adopted an artificial personality,\N taking the form of a young girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What would you think about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.12,0:16:29.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Such a monster is attempting \Nto mingle in our society, in disguise.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.59,0:16:30.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.68,0:16:33.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Kashimura{-san}, since meeting her,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.23,0:16:36.72,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,have you or your granddaughter\N been in mortal danger?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.72,0:16:39.29,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't listen to a word she says!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.32,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, everything you're saying is—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.78,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Zouroku...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.50,0:16:50.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think it's true that I'm a monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.83,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There are lots of things I thought were strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.83,0:16:53.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.88,0:17:00.36,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If you find out what I really am,\N I'm sure you'll hate me, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.36,0:17:03.35,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,M-Maybe you already hate me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.96,0:17:11.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I don't want you or Sanae to go through\N any more trouble because of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.14,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sana...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.14,0:17:16.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,If it was all because I wanted to be human,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.39,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,then you don't... need me around.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Zouroku.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.25,0:17:25.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll go back to the research facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.62,0:17:29.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The food was delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.13,0:17:36.75,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a helicopter there!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.07,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go on my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.20,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That'll be faster.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.37,0:17:47.26,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you're so badass!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I found out which boat they're on.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.69,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Ichijou{-kun} will save them in no time.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.99,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine, really.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.99,0:18:00.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Right now, I bet your grandpa's \Nlecturing the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.93,0:18:04.89,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,He's saying, "I hate crooked stuff!"
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.20,0:18:11.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What're you making?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,They're graves.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.48,0:18:22.45,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,{\t(2995,3955,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}I don't clearly remember
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.10,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,what Grandpa said to me then.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.15,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.60,0:18:32.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when he said that Sana{-chan} \Nmight become part of our family,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.66,0:18:39.11,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I had a really strange feeling,\Nlike something tightening in my chest.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.67,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.23,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that it made me remember a little bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.52,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What Grandpa told me back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.17,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,at the time of my parents' funeral.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And how much his words saved me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.66,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.68,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.68,0:19:05.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if you aren't human, so what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.91,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say such dumb things.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.74,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Just come home with me now, Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said your name's Miriam{-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.65,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You said this girl isn't human.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.79,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then, let me ask... What is a human?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.79,0:19:29.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You shot a child, without a thought. \NCan you be considered human?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.81,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That is not the issue here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.34,0:19:36.12,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You're right that this girl's dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.12,0:19:39.24,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,The moment I take my eyes off her, \Nshe's causing a commotion.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.19,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,At best, she's a nuisance.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.84,0:19:45.28,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,But everyone does those things.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.61,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,As long as you see the problem\N and improve, it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.00,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.42,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she's happy when she has good food.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.63,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In her own clumsy way, she worries about others.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,And she even gauges others' moods.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.54,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Even when she's caused trouble,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.59,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,she's never done anything with malicious intent.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.47,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,That's who Sana is.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,She's got a heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.52,0:20:13.94,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,As I was saying, the issue here\N is not such a personal matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.94,0:20:16.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You aren't in any position to do anything with her—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.44,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Listen when your elders speak!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.98,0:20:24.03,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,All of us, no matter who, are imperfect somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,There are things we can't know or do on our own,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.95,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,so we lean on each other to get by.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true for you, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.90,0:20:38.92,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Look, even if this girl is some \Nkind of alien, like you say,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.84,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,is that really a problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.84,0:20:45.25,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You honestly don't think coexistence is possible?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.31,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Zouroku...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.65,0:20:52.08,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm not human, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.90,0:20:58.01,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll cause a lot of trouble for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,For Sanae, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.22,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.87,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,No matter what you are,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.87,0:21:06.53,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,in tough times, you should be with others.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.49,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't force yourself, Sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.09,0:21:17.40,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,In any case, I have no reason to send \Nyou away with these violent fools!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.19,0:21:21.70,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,You left because you wanted \Nto see what was outside, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.06,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Then do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.06,0:21:25.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't go back on your word.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.05,0:21:29.97,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I hate crooked stuff, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.93,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Y-You must be an idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.93,0:21:40.90,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.63,0:21:51.16,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.51,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm here to save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.12,0:21:59.86,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm Cabinet Information Research Office \NSecret Service agent Ichijou Shizuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.89,0:22:04.09,GJM_Main_1080p,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking you two with us!
